{"tid":2014083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【第卅柒期牆紙】 軍政府","createTime":"2020-05-12T18:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T05:33:05.000Z","uid":253119,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"fa7762aba3caa8bd3e0347acb322e992ba1c4dce","tid":2014083,"uid":253119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T18:36:00.000Z","msg":"疫情的熱度稍稍過去，抗爭的節奏卷土重來，但敵人從未放鬆，內委會的爭議、即將二讀的國歌法，都把香港繼續捲往漩渦更深處。<br />\n<br />\n社會上不同層面都充斥著惡，警方的醜聞層出不窮、懲教酷刑亦積日已深，議會暴力的本質示於人前。那座被火燒的鐵皮屋子的火勢愈是猛烈了，有些人早已清醒過來，盼那些依然沉睡的得以驚醒，看看社會的搖搖欲墜。面對撕破臉皮的獸，以往的舊慣，也許應作出改變。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n目錄<br />\n1. 內委會爭議：我們是如何理解「議會」？ <br />\n2. 認罪無罪<br />\n3. 比路西法更惡&mdash;&mdash;懲教酷刑<br />\n4. 廢校「詐」彈案<br />\n5. 陶輝檔案 <br />\n6. 【立會候選人入】初選之後怎樣？<br />\n7. 建制 ｜獻世  <br />\n8. Rule Die Twice<br />\n9. 原罪民 <br />\n10. Why We Must Stop Indulging in the Pure Idea of Independence<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n點擊連結用投稿衝擊牆紙：@wallpaperneedyou<br />\n<br />\n#37期 #37th<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bceUv7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbceUv7g.jpg&h=5905d2d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qqoaOTY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqqoaOTY.jpg&h=84465dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EaKM6FE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEaKM6FE.jpg&h=b6f42df2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XhOx2d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXhOx2d0.jpg&h=fb4e22a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZQb38T2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQb38T2.jpg&h=920d1216&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgYx2d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?